    <section class="guide-page-section advantages">
        <h3>Advantages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Quicker to create the app.</li>
            <li>Can usually share over 90% of the app code between platforms.</li>
            <li>Can mix and match between React Native and "Real" native where needed.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="guide-page-section disadvantages">
        <h3>Disadvantages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Not officially support by Apple or Google.</li>
